== Characters ==

Name: Bernard Benedict Bailey
Birthdate: July 1st 1842
Bio:
Bernard was born in Newark, New Jersey. He sided with the Union and participated in the Civil War. Right before the war, he fell in love with Ashley, and promised to marry her.
Whenever he does an arrogant act, it leads to greater trouble for his party.

